# Ansible playbook

This playbook installs the NVIDIA drivers and tools to work with GPU's within a VM. 
Currently its based on the Grid K2 setup im working with. 

Goals of this playbooks is to place drivers, benchmarks, examples and test environment. 

# Since packer sets up the VM with an apt update after its initial boot, please be aware that the first step can fail due to dpkg db being in use.